{"actor":"charly vibes","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T19:58:06Z","event_type":"updated","id":165,"issue_id":"nayra-mtt","new_value":"{\"description\":\"The justfile refers to 'npm run build', but this script is missing from package.json. Recommendation: Add a build script that prepares the dist/ directory. Suggestion: Use a minimal tool like 'esbuild' or a simple minifier that preserves ES6 module compatibility. Acceptance: 'npm run build' generates a functional 'dist/' directory. CRITICAL: Follow TDD and Tidy First.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"nayra-mtt\",\"title\":\"Add build script to package.json\",\"description\":\"The justfile refers to 'npm run build', but this script is missing from package.json. Recommendation: Add a build script that prepares the dist/ directory. CRITICAL: Follow TDD and Tidy First.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"charly.vibes@proton.me\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T22:55:44Z\",\"created_by\":\"charly vibes\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T22:55:44Z\"}"}
